The package boost-circular-buffer is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS circular_buffer)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::circular_buffer)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_circular_buffer REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::circular_buffer)
